author: Alexandr Peterberg
text:
It's been two months and still no Undertale stream. If Rushia did give up on it, then I guess her determination is nowhere as strong as other members of Hololive have. If she hasn't given up, she still showcases to us how weak her determination is by not dedicating herself to beating Sans and finishing the G route.

Guess the ending of the G route is something we won't ever see happen in this channel.
